y/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0734","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0734.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0934","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 命令注入漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在输入参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）可绕过程序限制，读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Greg Matthews 开发的 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 版本，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0934"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.560","remediation":"升级到 Classifieds.cgi 2.0 或更高版本，对用户输入的所有参数进行严格过滤，移除 shell 元字符（如 `;` `|` `&` `$` 等），或改用 Perl 的 `sysread`/`syswrite` 而非反引号调用系统命令。如该脚本已无人维护，建议替换为受支持的现代 Web 应用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2020","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20444"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0734.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0935","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 1.0 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 CGI 表单的隐藏变量中插入恶意命令，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Greg Matthews 开发的 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 版本，由于程序未对隐藏变量参数进行充分过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可构造特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，从而实现远程命令执行，完全控制目标服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0935"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.687","remediation":"该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即从 Web 服务器移除 classifieds.cgi 脚本，或替换为现代且受支持的分类广告系统（如 OsClass 或 WordPress 分类插件）。如无法立即移除，可将脚本所在目录添加至 Apache 的 Deny from all 规则或 Nginx 的 deny all 配置以禁用访问。同时检查 Web 服务器日志排查是否已被利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0935","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20442"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1681","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1681.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0996","title":"Infoseek Ultraseek GET请求缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1/3.1 for NT 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 GET 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1 及 3.1 for Windows NT 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。无需身份认证即可远程利用，属于典型的基于栈的缓冲区溢出。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0996"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.210","remediation":"立即升级至 Infoseek Ultraseek 3.1 以上版本（如 4.x/5.x 系列），该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。由于 Infoseek 产品线已停止维护，建议迁移至现代搜索引擎解决方案（如 Elasticsearch、Apache Solr 等）。临时缓解措施可在反向代理或 Web 服务器层面限制 GET 请求长度，并对输入参数进行长度校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD19991215.html","http://www.osvdb.org/6490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19679","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0996","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0996.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j7c5-2gh9-m7cm/GHSA-j7c5-2gh9-m7cm.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/ultraseek_detect.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1681.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0858","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1010","title":"OpenSSH 1.2.27 不允许的 none 加密算法绕过漏洞","description":"SSH 1.2.27 服务器存在安全策略绕过漏洞。攻击者在 SSH 连接协商阶段可强制请求使用 \"none\" 加密算法，即使服务器端策略禁止无加密连接，服务器仍会接受该请求并建立未加密会话。远程攻击者无需任何认证即可利用此漏洞，绕过服务器的安全加密策略，获取明文传输的敏感数据或对通信内容进行中间人攻击。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1010"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.990","remediation":"升级 OpenSSH 至 2.1 或更高版本，SSH1 协议存在此设计缺陷，建议完全禁用 SSH1 协议并仅使用 SSH2。在 sshd_config 中设置 Protocol 2 并添加 Ciphers aes256-ctr,aes192-ctr,aes128-ctr 限制加密算法。如无法升级，在 sshd_config 中显式设置 Ciphers !none 禁用无加密连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94519142415338&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1010","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv.json","https://github.com/phx/cvescan/blob/d8d463e490d1d2d785179e8ace7ff59c2ea15f1f/README.md","https://github.com/privy-cafe/DollarLinuxClub/blob/57ae5d72b23dd6fe9fc5fca4dd120ffdf9dca123/misc/efnetretards.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0842","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0842.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1003","title":"Jgaa WarFTPd 1.70 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"War FTP Daemon (WarFTPd) 1.70 存在连接洪水拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 FTP 服务发送大量并发连接请求，耗尽服务器连接池与系统资源，导致 FTP 服务崩溃或无法响应正常用户请求。该漏洞影响 WarFTPd 1.70 版本，攻击条件简单，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1003"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.130","remediation":"升级至 WarFTPd 1.80 及以上版本（1.80 改进了连接处理机制），或在防火墙层面为 TCP 端口 21 配置连接速率限制（如 iptables 的 connlimit 模块限制单 IP 最大并发连接数）。由于该软件已停止维护，建议迁移至 FileZilla Server 或 vsftpd 等持续维护的 FTP 服务端软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1003","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1003.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1003.md","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/1999/database/CVE-1999-1003/README.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1003.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1003.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88372/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/im23pds/CVE-2019-1003000-and-CVE-2018-1999002-Pre-Auth-RCE-Jenkins"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0842.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0854","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0854.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1007","title":"VDO VDOLive Player 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VDO Live Player 3.0.2 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送特制的 .vdo 文件触发该漏洞，导致在受害者客户端上执行任意命令。攻击者只需诱导用户打开恶意构造的 .vdo 媒体文件即可完成利用，无需身份认证，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1007"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.627","remediation":"VDOLive Player 3.0.2 已停止维护且无官方安全补丁，建议立即卸载该软件，改用 VLC、Windows Media Player 等仍在受支持的媒体播放器。如需继续使用，可通过防火墙和组策略限制该程序对网络资源的访问权限，并避免打开来源不明的 .vdo 文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94512259331599&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/872","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19678","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1007","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1007.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0854.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1668","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0993","title":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 ACLs 访问控制漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在访问控制漏洞，管理员对访问控制列表（ACL）的修改不会立即生效，需等待目录存储缓存刷新后才能应用。在此期间，系统实际运行的访问控制规则与预期配置不一致，可能导致已被修改权限的用户在缓存刷新前仍可访问本应受限的资源。攻击者可利用此时间窗口绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问权限，影响系统机密性与完整性。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0993"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.833","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 Post-SP3 安全更新（即 Exchange 5.5 SP3 之后发布的累积安全修补程序）。临时缓解措施：修改 ACL 后手动重启 Microsoft Exchange Directory Service（DS），或在注册表中调低目录存储缓存刷新间隔（HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\MSExchangeDS\\Parameters\\Cache Refresh Interval（秒））以加速生效。根本解决建议升级至受支持的 Exchange 2016/2019 版本，Exchange 5.5 已停止支持多年，不推荐继续使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0020","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0289","title":"Apache HTTP Server Win32 附加点号致信息泄露漏洞","description":"Apache Web Server for Win32 存在文件访问控制绕过漏洞。当攻击者在请求 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.）时，服务器可能绕过正常权限检查，导致受限制文件被未授权访问。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞读取目标系统中的敏感文件（如配置文件、密码文件等），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Apache for Win32 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0289"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.840","remediation":"升级到 Apache 1.3.12 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 1.3.x 后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 Apache 配置中使用 `RewriteRule` 或 `AliasMatch` 拒绝所有以 `.` 结尾的 URL 请求，或在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面过滤 URL 末尾的 `.` 字符作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0289.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/798e84e356727c60a18eb3d0b86fb61b9862fb74/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w6fh-wrw4-q6vg/GHSA-w6fh-wrw4-q6vg.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/Xilinx/meta-openembedded/blob/4d3e2639dec542b58708244662d5ce36810fc510/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.66.bb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0857","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0857.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1009","title":"Disney Go Express Search 远程信息访问与修改漏洞","description":"Disney Go Express Search 存在信息泄露与未授权访问漏洞。该软件在用户系统上运行 HTTP 服务器，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络连接访问该服务，窃取或篡改用户的搜索信息。攻击者利用此漏洞可获取用户搜索记录等敏感数据，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。受影响用户需关闭该服务或采取防火墙规则限制外部访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1009"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.870","remediation":"立即卸载 Disney Go Express Search 程序，该软件已停止维护且不再有安全更新。可通过 Windows 的\"添加/删除程序\"功能进行卸载。卸载后检查系统是否有残留的 HTTP 服务进程，确保端口未被非法占用。临时缓解措施可在防火墙中阻止该程序的所有入站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1009.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000932.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0857.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0773","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0773.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0975","title":"Microsoft Windows 帮助文件本地命令执行漏洞","description":"Windows 帮助系统存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过编辑具有 .CNT 扩展名的目录内容元文件（contents metafile），将其中的主题操作（topic action）修改为待执行命令。当其他用户访问对应的 .hlp 帮助文件时，该命令即被触发执行，从而实现以目标用户身份执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 等版本，利用需要本地访问权限，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0975"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.610","remediation":"升级到不受此漏洞影响的 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统。如无法升级，可删除或重命名 C:\\Windows\\Hlp95.exe（Windows 95/98）或 C:\\Winnt\\System32\\Winhlp32.exe（Windows NT 4.0）以禁用帮助系统，或通过组策略/注册表限制 .cnt 文件与 winhlp32.exe 的文件关联。同时建议禁用从不受信任来源下载 .hlp/.cnt 文件的功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/868","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19673"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0773.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1509","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0977","title":"Sun Solaris sadmind 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 Solstice AdminSuite 管理守护进程 sadmind 存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 2325 端口发送特制的 NETMGT_PROC_SERVICE 请求触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多版本 Solaris 操作系统，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0977"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 (Patch ID: 106235-01 及后续更新)，或升级到受支持的 Solaris 版本。如非业务必需，建议禁用 sadmind 服务，并在网络层面通过防火墙限制对 111/TCP 和 111/UDP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/191","http://www.osvdb.org/2558","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2354","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/866","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/213"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/213"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/213"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0758","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0758.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0972","title":"WolfPack Development Xshipwars 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WolfPack Development 出品的 XSHIPWARS 是一款在线太空战斗游戏，其 xsw 程序存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长数据包触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致远程代码执行或服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 XSHIPWARS 1.0 及 1.2.4 版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0972"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.220","remediation":"WolfPack Development 已于 2000 年代初停止维护 XSHIPWARS，官方未发布任何安全补丁。建议立即卸载该软件，或在无法卸载时在防火墙层面限制外部主机对 xsw 服务端口（默认 UDP/TCP 端口）的访问，仅允许可信局域网 IP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/863","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19667"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0758.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0784","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0784.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0978","title":"debian_linux htdig 代码执行漏洞（攻击者可通过文件名中的 shell 元字符远程执行命令）","description":"htdig 搜索引擎软件在处理文件名参数时未正确过滤 shell 元字符，导致远程攻击者可通过构造包含 shell 元字符（如反引号、分号、管道符等）的恶意文件名参数，注入并执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Debian Linux 等发行版中包含 htdig 搜索引擎的版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，通过构造恶意搜索请求或文件上传请求，可在服务器上以 Web 服务进程权限执行任意命令，导致服务器完全沦陷。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。Debian 官方已发布安全更新修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0978"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.983","remediation":"建议将 htdig 升级至 3.1.5 及以上版本，该版本已修复 htsearch CGI 对文件名中 shell 元字符处理不当的问题。若暂时无法升级，应对传入 htsearch 的 config、restrict、exclude 等参数进行严格过滤，禁止 `;`、`|`、`&`、`` ` ``、`$()` 等特殊字符，并将 CGI 以最小权限运行。Debian 用户可执行 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade 安装官方修复包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/867"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0784.toml"}]